Rosie

Rosie is a 9 year old siberian cat! She is very fluffy and lazy. She is not very playful and she likes to eat.

Stormy

Stormy is a rescue cat! he's around 5 months old. He is extremely playful and a little annoying. He is very cute though so we love him.
